        <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl mb-6 text-yellow-600">Kitchen Expertise</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/80 text-sm">
          <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Full Gut Remodels</li>
          <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Custom Island Installation</li>
          <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Pantry Organization Systems</li>
          <li class="border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Crown Molding & Trim</li>
